input.description:
Defines the headers for the REST POST request in the JSON format.

Sample:

{
"headers" :
        { 
        "headerName" : "headerValue",
        "authorization" :
            {
 	           "type" : "basic",
			"user-name" : "myUser",
			"password" : "myPassword"

			}
          }
}

The data to be used in POST, PUT or DELETE operations. NOT Applicable for GET Operation.


Sample Fomat for any JSON data:


	{
	--- any json ---
	}


Format for Multipart data:


	{
		"entry": [
        	{ "key":"", "value":"", "content-type":""},
        	{"key":"", "value":"", "content-type":""}
          ]
	}
